  "text": "Language assessment. Phonological processing and speech production abilities were measured using a subset of tests from the York Adult Assessment-Revised (YAA-R; [CITATION_1] . This test battery has been developed as a screening tool for diagnosing language and reading impairments, such as dyslexia, in students in higher education. Its inclusion here was to ensure comparable ability between patients and control on phonological and speech processing.",
